{"data":[{"name":"112:1","price":"Айт (оо, Мухаммад:) Ал – Аллах жалгыз!","arabic":"قُلۡ هُوَ ٱللَّهُ أَحَدٌ","category":["112 (Al-Ikhlas)","Al-Ikhlas","Surah Al-Ikhlas"],"ayahNumber":6222,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"qul huwa al-lahu aḥadun ","translations":["Say","He","(is) Allah","the One","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","huwa","al-lahu","aḥadun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,700],[3,700,1680],[4,1680,2915]]}},{"name":"112:2","price":"Аллах – Сомад (Беймуктаж)","arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ٱلصَّمَدُ","category":["112 (Al-Ikhlas)","Al-Ikhlas","Surah Al-Ikhlas"],"ayahNumber":6223,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"al-lahu al-ṣamadu ","translations":["Allah","the Eternal, the Absolute","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["al-lahu","al-ṣamadu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1050],[2,1050,2485]]}},{"name":"112:3","price":"Ал туубаган жана да туулбаган!","arabic":"لَمۡ يَلِدۡ وَلَمۡ يُولَدۡ","category":["112 (Al-Ikhlas)","Al-Ikhlas","Surah Al-Ikhlas"],"ayahNumber":6224,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"lam yalid walam yūlad ","translations":["Not","He begets","and not","He is begotten","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["lam","yalid","walam","yūlad",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1050],[3,1050,1740],[4,1740,2915]]}},{"name":"112:4","price":"Жана эч ким Ага тең эмес!","arabic":"وَلَمۡ يَكُن لَّهُۥ كُفُوًا أَحَدُۢ","category":["112 (Al-Ikhlas)","Al-Ikhlas","Surah Al-Ikhlas"],"ayahNumber":6225,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"walam yakun lahu kufuwan aḥadun ","translations":["And not","is","for Him","equivalent","any [one]","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["walam","yakun","lahu","kufuwan","aḥadun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,530],[2,530,1250],[3,1250,2080],[4,2080,3000],[5,3000,4695]]}},{"name":"113:1","price":"Айт (оо, Мухаммад): «Таң Раббисинен коргоо тилеймин:[1]","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡفَلَقِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6226,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] Ушул жана мындан кийинки - “Ан-Нас” сүрөлөрүнүн түшүүсүнө төмөнкү окуя себеп болгон: Лабид деген бир жөөт сыйкырчысы көралбастыктын айынан он бир даана түйүнчөккө дем салып, пайгамбарыбызды сыйкырлап койот. Мунун натыйжасында пайгамбарыбыз саллаллоху алайхи ва саллам бир аз унутчаак болуп калганда, Аллах таала “Фалак” жана “Ан-Нас” сүрөлөрүн түшүрүп, алар менен өзүнө дем салууга буюрат. Пайгамбарыбыз ар бир аятты окуган сайын бирден түйүн чечилип, сыйкырдан кутулат. Бул эки сүрөнү пайгамбарыбыз ар кандай жамандыктардан сактанууга жана ооруганда шыпаа болуу үчүн окуганы белгилүү.","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-falaqi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) the dawn","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-falaqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,360],[2,360,1280],[3,1280,2110],[4,2110,3005]]}},{"name":"113:2","price":"(Өзү) жараткан (зыяндуу) нерселердин жамандыгынан...,","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ مَا خَلَقَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6227,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri mā khalaqa ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) what","He created","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","mā","khalaqa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,2040],[3,2040,2380],[4,2380,3595]]}},{"name":"113:3","price":"Каптап кирген учурдагы (караңгы) түндүн жамандыгынан...,[1]","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ غَاسِقٍ إِذَا وَقَبَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6228,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] Караңгы кирээри менен жин-шайтандар жайылып, ар кандай жамандыктар көбөйөт.","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ghāsiqin idhā waqaba ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) darkness","when","it spreads","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ghāsiqin","idhā","waqaba",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,740],[2,740,2140],[3,2140,3250],[4,3250,3870],[5,3870,4945]]}},{"name":"113:4","price":"Түйүндөргө дем салган сайкырчылардын жамандыгынан...,","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ ٱلنَّفَّٰثَٰتِ فِي ٱلۡعُقَدِ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6229,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri al-nafāthāti fī al-ʿuqadi ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) the blowers","in","the knots","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","al-nafāthāti","fī","al-ʿuqadi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2150],[3,2150,4440],[4,4440,4630],[5,4630,5935]]}},{"name":"113:5","price":"Сугун арткан учурда, көрө албаган кишинин жамандыгынан.[1]","arabic":"وَمِن شَرِّ حَاسِدٍ إِذَا حَسَدَ","category":["113 (Al-Falaq)","Al-Falaq","Surah Al-Falaq"],"ayahNumber":6230,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] Эгер мусулман пенде кимдир бирөөнүн сук назарынан шектенсе, ушул сүрөнү окуйт. Анткени, кээ бир адамдардын сук назары адамга зыян кылышы мүмкүн. Муну эл арасында «көз тийди» деп коюшат. Бул аят көз тийиши акыйкат экенине далил. Пайгамбарыбыздын таалими боюнча, өзүн таң калтырган нерсени көргөн адам “ма шаа Аллаху, табаарак Аллаху” (Аллахтын каалаганы болот, Аллах эң Ыйык) деген дубаны окушу керек. Ошондо анын назары өзүн кызыктырган нерсеге (же адамга) зыян кылбайт.","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"wamin sharri ḥāsidin idhā ḥasada ","translations":["And from","(the) evil","(of) an envier","when","he envies","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wamin","sharri","ḥāsidin","idhā","ḥasada",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,500],[2,500,1990],[3,1990,3160],[4,3160,3750],[5,3750,5605]]}},{"name":"114:1","price":"Айткын (оо, Мухаммад): «Мен инсандардын Раббисинен","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6231,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-nāsi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) mankind","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,330],[2,330,1230],[3,1230,2050],[4,2050,6085]]}},{"name":"114:2","price":"Инсандардын падышасынан;","arabic":"مَلِكِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6232,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"maliki al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) King","(of) mankind","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["maliki","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,5205]]}},{"name":"114:3","price":"инсандардын (сыйынууга татыктуу болгон) Кудайынан коргоо тилеймин –","arabic":"إِلَٰهِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6233,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"ilāhi al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) God","(of) mankind","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ilāhi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,5295]]}},{"name":"114:4","price":"(Аллахтын ысымы айтылганда) жашынып калуучунун[1] жамандыгынан.","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ ٱلۡوَسۡوَاسِ ٱلۡخَنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6234,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] Шайтандын.","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri al-waswāsi al-khanāsi ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) the whisperer","the one who withdraws","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","al-waswāsi","al-khanāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2119],[3,2119,3389],[4,3389,7914]]}},{"name":"114:5","price":"Ал (шайтан) адамдардын көкүрөгүнө азгырык салат.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُوَسۡوِسُ فِي صُدُورِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6235,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yuwaswisu fī ṣudūri al-nāsi ","translations":["The one who","whispers","in","(the) breasts","(of) mankind","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yuwaswisu","fī","ṣudūri","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2130],[3,2130,2510],[4,2510,3420],[5,3420,7865]]}},{"name":"114:6","price":"Алар (азгыруучу шайтандар) жиндерден жана адамдардан болот.[1]","arabic":"مِنَ ٱلۡجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6236,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] Аллах таала Куранда инсандарды ак жолдон азгырган адамдарды да «шайтан» деп атайт.","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-jinati wal-nāsi ","translations":["From","the jinn","and men","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-jinati","wal-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,2610],[3,2610,8185]]}},{"name":"109:1","price":"(Оо, Мухаммад, каапырларга) айткын: «Эй, каапырлар!","arabic":"قُلۡ يَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلۡكَٰفِرُونَ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6208,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"qul yāayyuhā al-kāfirūna ","translations":["Say","O","disbelievers","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","yāayyuhā","al-kāfirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,3370],[3,3370,7425]]}},{"name":"109:2","price":"Мен силер ибадат кылган(кудайлар)га ибадат кылбаймын!","arabic":"لَآ أَعۡبُدُ مَا تَعۡبُدُونَ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6209,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"lā aʿbudu mā taʿbudūna ","translations":["Not","I worship","what","you worship","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["lā","aʿbudu","mā","taʿbudūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2590],[2,2590,3460],[3,3460,3840],[4,3840,7365]]}},{"name":"109:3","price":"Силер дагы мен сыйынганга (Аллах таалага) сыйынуучу эмессиңер.","arabic":"وَلَآ أَنتُمۡ عَٰبِدُونَ مَآ أَعۡبُدُ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6210,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"walā antum ʿābidūna mā aʿbudu ","translations":["And not","you","(are) worshippers","(of) what","I worship","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","antum","ʿābidūna","mā","aʿbudu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2380],[2,2380,3760],[3,3760,5090],[4,5090,6920],[5,6920,8155]]}},{"name":"109:4","price":"Мен силер ибадат кылган кудайларга сыйынбаймын!","arabic":"وَلَآ أَنَا۠ عَابِدٞ مَّا عَبَدتُّمۡ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6211,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"walā anā ʿābidun mā ʿabadttum ","translations":["And not","I am","a worshipper","(of) what","you worship","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","anā","ʿābidun","mā","ʿabadttum",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2320],[2,2320,2700],[3,2700,3630],[4,3630,4990],[5,4990,6325]]}},{"name":"109:5","price":"Силер да мен ибадат кылган(Аллах таала)га ибадат кылуучу эмессиңер.","arabic":"وَلَآ أَنتُمۡ عَٰبِدُونَ مَآ أَعۡبُدُ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6212,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"walā antum ʿābidūna mā aʿbudu ","translations":["And not","you","(are) worshippers","(of) what","I worship","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","antum","ʿābidūna","mā","aʿbudu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2120],[2,2120,3780],[3,3780,5230],[4,5230,7070],[5,7070,8365]]}},{"name":"109:6","price":"(Демек,) силерге өз диниңер, мага өз диним!»","arabic":"لَكُمۡ دِينُكُمۡ وَلِيَ دِينِ","category":["109 (Al-Kafirun)","Al-Kafirun","Surah Al-Kafirun"],"ayahNumber":6213,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ky","meta":{"transliteration":"lakum dīnukum waliya dīni ","translations":["For you","(is) your religion","and for me","(is) my religion","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["lakum","dīnukum","waliya","dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1720],[3,1720,2510],[4,2510,5465]]}}],"dua":{"id":2,"name":"Four Quls (Al-Arba' Qul)","arabicName":"الأربع قل","reference":"112:1-4, 113:1-5, 114:1-6, 109:1-6","verseTitle":"The Four Declarations of Divine Oneness and Protection","significanceReason":"Considered a complete spiritual protection and declaration of divine unity, represent spiritual protection, affirmation of divine oneness, rejection of polytheism, and seeking refuge from all forms of harm, recited for spiritual defense, mental peace, and as a comprehensive protection against negative energies, jealousy, and spiritual afflictions."},"version":{"key":"kyrgyz_hakimov","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ky","version":"1.0.2","last_update":1708440100,"title":"Kyrgyz translation","description":"Translation of the meanings of the Noble Qur’an into the Kyrgyz language, translated by Shams al-Din Hakimov Abd al-Khaleq, reviewed and developed under the supervision of the Rowad Translation Center."}}